The '''Pirates of Tarnoonga''' was a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] group based on [[Tarnoonga/Legends|Tarnoonga]], and led by [[Gir Kybo Ren-Cha]].

Their forces consist of the [[Gladiator-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Gladiator''-class star Destroyer]] ''[[Demolisher]]'', the [[Dianoga (starship)|''Dianoga'']], and several custom-painted TIE Fighters.

